column1: herre-wieger-roelevink-5611b83,Herre Wieger,Roelevink,"Helping our clients with additional software development capacity with our team of experienced Laravel/PHP, React, Magento, Node.js, Ruby on Rails and Mobile App developers.",https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C4E03AQHx5I2xN0pFGQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1538011143938?e=1697673600&v=beta&t=1upGPhQllDAITYalVbVt7VE_fbUcdgyMaWwIFZL6jZY,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C4E16AQHCYqIjJhMFtw/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/0/1661328494958?e=1697673600&v=beta&t=UlETJFn_Io-pQaXWl5jMhBKcBeMA3TVXxFSHPXvLLEg,personal,ACoAAACQMBkBJzoOjmXITd-086RZnVdlbO9EM34,9449497,,"Manifera is an international software development company with offices in Singapore and Vietnam.
We provide the following services to our appreciated clients:

To expand your company’s software development capacity in an easy and cost-effective way, we can provide you with a team of software developers who act as your own extended team. You will have full control of the developers and you will work with the developers directly and daily.

With our custom software development services we can help you design and develop the right software application for your business needs, based on your requirements and ideas. We develop web applications, mobile applications for iOS and Android and desktop applications.
Benefits of Manifera for your Benefit:

column2: Developers experienced with many technologies like: Laravel/PHP, React, Python, Magento, Ruby on Rails, and many more.
Custom made full stack software development solutions, providing DevOps and Service and Maintenance as well.
We provide our services in an environment based upon trust and mutual respect, by which attaining many long-term clients.
Easy, fast and affordable setup of your own offshore software development team.
The fusion of Western Management with Vietnamese Mastery leads to great achievements for our clients.
Your own Offshore Software Development Team

column1: We work with SMEs from Europe, USA and South East Asia. With our team of experienced software developers, quality engineers and project managers we provide our clients with Offshore Software Development teams and custom made software application development services.
